{"tid":1290134,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 連儂牆 香港人加油！","createTime":"2019-07-06T11:27:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T06:27:21.000Z","uid":67844,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"2e94e884a9e84c3c33ebdc7d0e8be0cbc2fbf0cc","tid":1290134,"uid":67844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:27:36.000Z","msg":"連儂牆已經逐漸係各區出現，大家經過既不彷留下字句鼓勵下香港人。 唔好睇小你既一字一句，可能就係因為你既一句令喱場運動多一個人或者多一個人會注意到！<br />\n<br />\n[/size=6]多你一個直係好多[/size=6]<br />\n<br />\n希望各位巴絲唔好介意，我只係係唔同post到cap圖落黎再group返埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BECJ7mq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBECJ7mq.png&h=1cb5e7f5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aB7J7ms.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaB7J7ms.png&h=b5aa0158&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jFALBeO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjFALBeO.png&h=60331482&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n六月好多唔開心既事發生左，但唯獨有一件事係值得開心既<br />\n就係每一次走上街頭都有好<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人</span>同我地一齊。終於唔洗日日出街再見到d大陸人<br />\n<br />\n韓國都要23次遊行，歷時半年先令朴槿惠落台<br />\n史上無一次革命係一次就成功！我地即管鬥長命！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香 港 人 加 油</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">77繼續不撤不散</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jsZAd5s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjsZAd5s.png&h=2e083a98&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"532c311bca61a9b7d24a23b07de7d670d3fdaab0","tid":1290134,"uid":42217,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-06T11:28:23.000Z","msg":"5p弟囝g持尼地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d583a347d33378b35f2725b906fb557f06f7f97","tid":1290134,"uid":33618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019